{"tid":1852020,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"每個人都會生病，不要因此而孤立中國人","createTime":"2020-01-30T09:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T13:17:32.000Z","uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"89113dfe068cb4356a321142e7e93225e6cf12eb","tid":1852020,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"分享加拿大🇨🇦学校发给所有家长的邮件，我觉得写得很好，转发： <br />\n<br />\nEveryone may get sick, so please don't isolate Chinese and anyone who is connected to China. You cannot discriminate against the patients, because this behavior will make those patients ashamed of themselves, so as to hide the illness, and reject to protect others. We are against the virus, not the Chinese. The more Emergency arise, the more need for calm, humanity, unity.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n每個人都會生病，不要因此而孤立中國人和任何你認為與中国有联系的人，更不要歧視生病的人，因为这样会讓生病的人為自己生病而羞耻，從而隱瞞病情。我們防的是病毒，而不是中國人。越是危難之時，越需要冷静理智,加油！💪❤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心啦繁體都唔打多隻 邊個信你呀<br />\n大陸人"},{"pid":"ae5c0a0d5c056f9d94421a5dfb95c4ab8b2c4121","tid":1852020,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"224424e778592b19ebe4a9e9158e3efdbcd699b4","tid":1852020,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"We are against the virus, not the Chinese.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8dddd67f31599096318d55995c74f172630d09","tid":1852020,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ae5c0a0d5c056f9d94421a5dfb95c4ab8b2c4121","tid":1852020,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"嗯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"我們防的是病毒，亦是中國人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" cla